effect_entries.effect: Inflicts regular damage.  Removes leech seed from the user, frees the user from bind, clamp, fire spin, magma storm, sand tomb, whirlpool, and wrap, and clears spikes, stealth rock, and toxic spikes from the user's side of the field.  If this move misses or has no effect, its effect doesn't activate.
effect_entries.short_effect: Frees the user from binding moves, removes Leech Seed, and blows away Spikes.

flavor_text_entries.flavor_text:
通过旋转来攻击对手。
还可以摆脱绑紧、紧束、
寄生种子和撒菱等招式。

回転して　相手を　攻撃する。
しめつける　まきつく　やどりぎのタネ
まきびし　なども　吹きとばせる。

A spin attack that can also eliminate such moves as
Bind, Wrap, Leech Seed, and Spikes.

Attacco rotante che elimina gli effetti di
mosse come Legatutto, Avvolgibotta, Punte
e Parassiseme.

Ataque giratorio que puede eliminar movimientos 
como Atadura, Constricción, Drenadoras y Púas.

Trifft das Ziel mit einer Dreh-Attacke. Befreit den
Anwender unter anderem von Wickel, Klammergriff,
Egelsamen und Stachler.

Une attaque tournoyante pouvant aussi annuler
par exemple Étreinte, Ligotage, Vampigraine ou
Picots.
